data.description: Stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with tons to offer! Main floor boasts formal living and dining rooms, cozy family room with fireplace and vaulted ceiling, kitchen with tons of cabinet space, and an additional room ideal for in-home gym or office. Top floor bedrooms including primary bedroom and bath with dual vanity, garden tub and walk-in shower. Walk-out patio overlooks lush backyard great for entertaining!
